    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desolation Seed</strong> survive in a virtual wasteland of global demise and environmental decay using  remote EEG powered UAV mechanics ..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/f82323cf536d547f8eaab84a4a17be1f.poster.avif?t=1769308525\" width=480 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/f82323cf536d547f8eaab84a4a17be1f.webm?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/f82323cf536d547f8eaab84a4a17be1f.mp4?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫  no storyline - no direction just exist and explore in a complete open world of disease</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > and desolation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Engage in environmental problem solving to progress through the diseased earth while  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  searching for sustenance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Communicate with the remnants of humanity while exploring endless labyrinths  <br>of societal ruin and be fully immersed in virtual desolation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫Humanity is a source of food</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e701df8889872edddf8fb72440057db3.poster.avif?t=1769308525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e701df8889872edddf8fb72440057db3.webm?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e701df8889872edddf8fb72440057db3.mp4?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Explore the endless wasteland of abandoned networks, urban ruins &amp; navigate the polluted expanse of ecological decay with intuitive and responsive UAV flight control</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ shoot your way through a Hobbesian wasteland of other entities scouring for survival competing for limited resources</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e41f6214631013c92fb4bffbad9c967e.poster.avif?t=1769308525\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e41f6214631013c92fb4bffbad9c967e.webm?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/e41f6214631013c92fb4bffbad9c967e.mp4?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Inspect objects as you traverse interconnected levels inspired by the</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   literature of BF Skinner and the Tower of Babel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Perma death</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ waste simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▫ Survival Mechanics </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/abef3e0becc628983668aba40a237e88.poster.avif?t=1769308525\" width=500 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/abef3e0becc628983668aba40a237e88.webm?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818470/extras/abef3e0becc628983668aba40a237e88.mp4?t=1769308525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>* Some information above is subject to update as development progresses. follow page for frequent updates</strong></i></p>",
